Package: CohortDAG
Title: DAG-Based Batch Cohort SQL Generation for OMOP CDM
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Adam", "Black", , "ablack3@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5576-8701")),
    person("Artem", "Gorbachev", , "artem.gorbachev@odysseusinc.com", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Generates optimized batch SQL for ATLAS/OHDSI cohort definitions
    using a directed acyclic graph (DAG) execution plan. Deduplicates shared
    computations across cohorts, translates ATLAS JSON to SQL without Java/CirceR,
    and supports incremental caching with Merkle-tree validation.
